  "hint": "Inputs are [T, CLK, Load, D]. When Load=0, D_input = T XOR Q (toggle). When Load=1, D_input = D (parallel load). Use a MUX: MUX(sel=Load, d0=XOR(T,Q), d1=D) → DFF(D_input, CLK). The XOR uses the DFF's Q output as feedback.",
